{"tid":2273373,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【港講藝術】深夜時分，陪你看Doris Salcedo暴力式的裝置藝術","createTime":"2020-11-05T16:23:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T15:56:22.000Z","uid":17335,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2e2b9391c6b32e3bcd6710742d0be998bf316fb8","tid":2273373,"uid":17335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T16:23:31.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\">回不去了的傷痕，藝術家如何表現社會的撕裂？<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.guim.co.uk/img/static/Guardian/arts/gallery/2007/oct/08/1/GD4925419@'Shibboleth',-by-Colo-1682.jpg?width=700&amp;quality=85&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=max&amp;s=98c6e8fc8aec5a856704d40c1c6c008c\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.guim.co.uk%2Fimg%2Fstatic%2FGuardian%2Farts%2Fgallery%2F2007%2Foct%2F08%2F1%2FGD4925419%40%27Shibboleth%27%2C-by-Colo-1682.jpg%3Fwidth%3D700%26quality%3D85%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dmax%26s%3D98c6e8fc8aec5a856704d40c1c6c008c&h=20450e7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</p><br />\n二十一世紀才剛開始，我們都已踏入亂世，香港反送中，臺灣韓國瑜、美國大選&hellip;&hellip;彷彿，以往沒有浮現，累積的對立，火山爆發般，人人自危，彼此猜疑。<br />\n<br />\nDoris Salcedo（多麗絲&bull;薩爾塞多）早在2007年，已經以簡單粗暴的方式，用一條裂縫訴說着種族的隔離和仇恨，直指社會對立，對我們造成的創傷。<br />\n<br />\n裝置藝術「Shibboleth 」（暗語），Doris受Tate Modern藝術館委託而創作，她的藝術品最終耗資了30萬英鎊，竟把藝術館大廳的整個地面鋤爛，暴力式創作出一條長167米的裂縫！<br />\n<br />\n這一整條裂縫深度與寬度各不相同，裂縫最寬的開口有30 cm闊，一不留神，行人隨時會差錯腳。尼采的網路名句：「當你凝視深淵，深淵也同時凝視著你。」細看裂縫之黑暗，觀眾可以清晰地看到地面之下的鋼筋水泥結構，相當嚇人。<br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://artwithapurposeblog.files.wordpress.com/2016/10/34.jpg?w=1200&amp;h=768&amp;crop=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fartwithapurposeblog.files.wordpress.com%2F2016%2F10%2F34.jpg%3Fw%3D1200%26h%3D768%26crop%3D1&h=13863390&s={SIZE}\" /></p><br />\n平面上的線，深、闊都有象徵。Doris曾被問及，它的深到底有多深？「沒有底，它就像人性一樣深不可測。」<br />\n<br />\n此外，她亦提及此作代表了國家邊界，以歷史複雜的哥倫比亞為現實取材，當中非法移民、種族隔離、社會仇恨等議題，化繁為簡式呈現。<br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4b/Shibboleth_remains_IMG_1389.JPG/440px-Shibboleth_remains_IMG_1389.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F4%2F4b%2FShibboleth_remains_IMG_1389.JPG%2F440px-Shibboleth_remains_IMG_1389.JPG&h=9e9d3fe9&s={SIZE}\" /></p><br />\n裂痕就像一道傷疤，就算填補過後，還是會永遠烙印在藝術館大廳的地下。<br />\n<br />\n正如香港人曾唱：「何以這土地，淚再流？」Doris有關土地的藝術作品，象徵意涵可以相當普世，這件裝置藝術出色之處，除了寫實，亦能夠深深撼動，每個見證裂縫的人。<br />\n<br />\n生於亂世 ，裂縫無處不在，我們彷彿都看著地面分成兩邊，對錯是非，自有公論。可是這一條，這一條社會之間的傷痕，觸目驚心，就算日後有誰來修補，有誰來掩飾，仍然會永遠存在這一代香港人的心中。<br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/a8/30/02/a830029040216cd8e8404112ed4a34b5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2Fa8%2F30%2F02%2Fa830029040216cd8e8404112ed4a34b5.jpg&h=7ec18449&s={SIZE}\" /></p>"},{"pid":"e2f6cc55d02d0497bc6e74c84ad74b6dd3b5d82c","tid":2273373,"uid":6454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T16:23:56.000Z","msg":"sofa"},{"pid":"b54efae619e2faf1e2489a4cc3a7d429418202a2","tid":2273373,"uid":106336,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T16:24:45.000Z","msg":"呢個咪變咗一個永久嘅藝術品<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"223ac826dbf41c7dee6dc220a15b5841eeb443aa","tid":2273373,"uid":17335,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T16:25:40.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cNqaGX8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcNqaGX8.png&h=5285b833&s={SIZE}\" /></p><br />\n想睇更多文藝嘢，歡迎Follow德尼思化：<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nIG <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/delis.ver/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fdelis.ver%2F&d=RNNv2si1j6MvuJ657i5J8hSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=769be32f\" data-auto-